  "original_title": "\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bae\u0bc7\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd 6 \u0baa\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b85\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "6 more people have gone to Tamil Nadu as refugees",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "06 people from Jaffna and Kilinochchi district have gone to Tamil Nadu by sea and claimed refugee status.",
        "06 people including 5 people belonging to the same family living in Kilinochchi and one from Jaffna were taken away early on Wednesday morning at a place called Kampipad near Dhanushkodi in Tamil Nadu.",
        "The Coast Guard got information about it and rescued them, detained them at Mandapam Police Station and are conducting investigations.",
        "During investigations, they said that they had given the boat for 1 lakh 50 thousand rupees.",
        "Meanwhile, due to the severe economic downturn in Sri Lanka, the price of essential commodities such as rice, pulses and wheat has increased. Similarly, the prices of diesel and petrol have also increased significantly.",
        "One has to stand in line for 4 days to buy 2 liters of kerosene, continuous power cuts, shortage of medicine in government hospitals.",
        "Also, a bag of cement is being sold at 3,500 rupees, so the construction industry has been affected and they have no way to live because they cannot go to wage work.",
        "It is noteworthy that 129 Sri Lankan Tamils \u200b\u200bhave gone to Tamil Nadu as refugees from Sri Lanka since March 22nd till date due to economic crisis."
      ],
